EYE-SYNC uses high-performance, cutting-edge eye tracking technology to monitor eye movement in a handheld virtual reality environment. If your brain is out of sync after an on-field incident, SyncThinks technology will let you know in less than a minute.'),(91,80,'_add_first_sub_contain','field_569ddc8d75d8f'),(92,80,'add_second_sub_title','Screening and Recovery'),(93,80,'_add_second_sub_title','field_569ddd1b75d90'),(94,80,'add_second_sub_content','EYE-SYNC helps you with screening in the field and assessing return to play or work in the clinic'),(95,80,'_add_second_sub_content','field_569ddd3a75d91'),(96,80,'add_third_sub_title','Objective Testing'),(97,80,'_add_third_sub_title','field_569ddd5b75d92'),(98,80,'add_third_sub_content','EYE-SYNCs proven, transparent metrics evaluates a subjects eye-tracking performance stand alone or to their own baseline in a fast 60 second evaluation.'),(99,80,'_add_third_sub_content','field_569ddd6875d93'),(100,80,'add_fourth_sub_title','Durable hardware'),(101,80,'_add_fourth_sub_title','field_569ddd7575d94'),(102,80,'add_fourth_sub_content','Less than 5 pounds, EYE-SYNC is on the scene when you are.'),(103,80,'_add_fourth_sub_content','field_569ddd7c75d95'),(104,80,'add_product_image_1','95'),(105,80,'_add_product_image_1','field_569dde1d75d96'),(106,80,'add_product_image_2','96'),(107,80,'_add_product_image_2','field_569ddea075d97'),(108,80,'add_product_image_3','310'),(109,80,'_add_product_image_3','field_569ddeb375d98'),(110,80,'add_product_image_4','97'),(111,80,'_add_product_image_4','field_569ddec375d99'),(112,80,'add_product_image_5','99'),(113,80,'_add_product_image_5','field_569ddefe75d9a'),(114,80,'add_image','100'),(115,80,'_add_image','field_569de4890b1c8'),(116,80,'add_ghajar_title','Years of research, <strong>applied.</strong>'),(117,80,'_add_ghajar_title','field_569defa70b1c9'),(118,80,'add_ghajar_content','Dr. Jam Ghajar has dedicated his career to unlocking the mysteries behind concussions. EYE-SYNC is the culmination of years of research in the field by Dr. Ghajar and the Brain Trauma Foundation. See how EYE-SYNC changes the way he approaches concussion.'),(119,80,'_add_ghajar_content','field_569df0050b1ca'),(120,80,'visual_attention_pathways_0_add_title','Visual Attention Pathways'),(121,80,'_visual_attention_pathways_0_add_title','field_569df7b8bd8f4'),(122,80,'visual_attention_pathways_0_add_content','The brain whiplash from a force to the head impairs connections in the front of the brain. These connections are responsible for predicting what you are about to pay attention to. The result is a difficulty in predicting leading to problems in cognitive and motor activities such as athletics or classroom learning.'),(123,80,'_visual_attention_pathways_0_add_content','field_569df7cbbd8f5'),(124,80,'visual_attention_pathways_0_add__image','46'),(125,80,'_visual_attention_pathways_0_add__image','field_569df7e9bd8f6'),(126,80,'visual_attention_pathways','1'),(127,80,'_visual_attention_pathways','field_569df740bd8f3'),(128,80,'objective_attention_measurement_0_add_title','Objective Attention Measurement'),(129,80,'_objective_attention_measurement_0_add_title','field_569df826bd8f9'),(130,80,'objective_attention_measurement_0_add_content','Eye movement and attention share similar brain pathways. When brain connections are impaired in a concussion, variability in prediction occurs, leading to variability or jitter in visual performance. This same variability or jitter happens in thinking and movement but eye movement is the most accurate way of measurement it. State-of-the-art eye tracking goggles can measure prediction variability in less than a minute. Precision measurements allow clinicians to assess and track attention performance improvements during recovery.'),(131,80,'_objective_attention_measurement_0_add_content','field_569df864bd8fa'),(132,80,'objective_attention_measurement_0_add_slowrecovery_image','102'),(133,80,'_objective_attention_measurement_0_add_slowrecovery_image','field_569df87ebd8fb'),(134,80,'objective_attention_measurement_0_add_quickrecovery_image','103'),(135,80,'_objective_attention_measurement_0_add_quickrecovery_image','field_569df8cebd8fc'),(136,80,'objective_attention_measurement','1'),(137,80,'_objective_attention_measurement','field_569df817bd8f8'),(138,80,'quantifying_attention_0_add_title','Quantifying Attention'),(139,80,'_quantifying_attention_0_add_title','field_569df90bbd8fe'),(140,80,'quantifying_attention_0_add_content','										<p class=\"alignleft\">SyncThink metrics focus on predictive attention performance- key to everyday function. The EYE-SYNC records eye movement during a simple circular visual stimulus that lasts for 15 seconds and is repeated. The EYE-SYNC goggles immediately produces results showing variability in spatial and temporal prediction that is:</p>	\r\n										\r\n										<ul class=\"alignright\">\r\n											<li>\r\n												<p>Highly reliable with more than 0.8 test retest reliability</p>\r\n											</li>\r\n											\r\n											<li>\r\n												<p>No apparent effort or learning effect</p>\r\n											</li>\r\n											\r\n											<li>\r\n												<p>Useful for screening visual attention performance after a force to the head</p>\r\n											</li>\r\n											\r\n											<li>\r\n												<p>Determining recovery of impaired visual attention to return to work/play/school</p>\r\n											</li>\r\n										</ul>'),(141,80,'_quantifying_attention_0_add_content','field_569df938bd8ff'),(142,80,'quantifying_attention_0_add_image','104'),(143,80,'_quantifying_attention_0_add_image','field_569df948bd900'),(144,80,'quantifying_attention','1'),(145,80,'_quantifying_attention','field_569df8fcbd8fd'),(146,80,'thumbnail_image_0_add_title','Dynamic Attention'),(147,80,'_thumbnail_image_0_add_title','field_569dfa00bd903'),(148,80,'thumbnail_image_0_add_image','109'),(149,80,'_thumbnail_image_0_add_image','field_569dfa78bd904'),(150,80,'thumbnail_image