,'service_2_add_text_after_logo','is reliable.'),(570,125,'_service_2_add_text_after_logo','field_569e0786866f1'),(571,125,'service_2_add_content','SyncThink has tested its metrics on over 10,000 soldiers and athletes and shown a greater than 0.8 test-retest reliability - far exceeding other cognitive tests'),(572,125,'_service_2_add_content','field_569e07a3866f2'),(573,125,'service_2_add_thumbnail__image','113'),(574,125,'_service_2_add_thumbnail__image','field_569e07b9866f3'),(575,125,'service','3'),(576,125,'_service','field_569e075f866ef'),(577,125,'add_test_demo_title','Test Demo '),(578,125,'_add_test_demo_title','field_569e082f031e7'),(579,125,'add_test_demo_content','This is a demonstration of the actual test used in the EYE-SYNC technology. Hit play to see the test in real time - dont stray far, it takes less than a minute.'),(580,125,'_add_test_demo_content','field_569e0849031e8'),(581,125,'add_video_source','https://vimeo.com/141831446'),(582,125,'_add_video_source','field_569e0b0ead905'),(583,125,'add_video_image','114'),(584,125,'_add_video_image','field_569e0b6bad906'),(585,125,'add_environment_title','Where and when you need it'),(586,125,'_add_environment_title','field_569e0cf4ab817'),(587,125,'add_environment_sub_title','In the clinic or at the point of injury'),(588,125,'_add_environment_sub_title','field_569e0d2cab818'),(589,125,'add_environment_content','Cognitive assessment tools are tedious, inaccurate, or immobile. EYE-SYNC delivers world-class clinical tools from the playing field to the battlefield. Follow-up with the same toolset in a clinical setting to determine return-to-activity evaluation.'),(590,125,'_add_environment_content','field_569e0d3cab819'),(591,125,'slider_0_add_title','Clinic'),(592,125,'_slider_0_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(593,125,'slider_0_add_image','115'),(594,125,'_slider_0_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(595,125,'slider_0_add_over_text','The EYE-SYNC <br />follows patients from the<br /> field into the clinician\'s office.<br /> Our reliability and precision<br /> allows the user to track<br /> performance back to <br />recovery.'),(596,125,'_slider_0_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(597,125,'slider_1_add_title','Playing Field '),(598,125,'_slider_1_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(599,125,'slider_1_add_image','116'),(600,125,'_slider_1_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(601,125,'slider_1_add_over_text','Coaches and trainers <br /> need to make fast on-field<br /> decisions that might place an <br /> athlete in harm\'s way. The EYE-SYNC<br /> is a mobile, objective assessment <br /> that provides clarity after <br /> an injury.'),(602,125,'_slider_1_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(603,125,'slider_2_add_title','Battlefield'),(604,125,'_slider_2_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(605,125,'slider_2_add_image','117'),(606,125,'_slider_2_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(607,125,'slider_2_add_over_text','EYE-SYNC is a<br /> functional assessment that <br /> provides real-time information to <br /> commanders on the battlefield. Spot <br /> and care for injury before it <br /> becomes a danger to the <br />mission.'),(608,125,'_slider_2_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(609,125,'slider','3'),(610,125,'_slider','field_569e0d69ab81a'),(611,125,'list_0_image','118'),(612,125,'_list_0_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(613,125,'list_1_image','119'),(614,125,'_list_1_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(615,125,'list_2_image','120'),(616,125,'_list_2_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(617,125,'list','3'),(618,125,'_list','field_569e2e6719f96'),(619,125,'testimonial_0_add_background_image','121'),(620,125,'_testimonial_0_add_background_image','field_569f36bfb2f30'),(621,125,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_title','Stanford University'),(622,125,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_title','field_569f36a4b2f2f'),(623,125,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_image','123'),(624,125,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_image','field_569f36d9b2f31'),(625,125,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_content','Stanford Sports Medicine uses EYE-SYNC technology currently to screen athletes for concussion and make decisions on return to play.'),(626,125,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_content','field_569f36f7b2f32'),(627,125,'testimonial_0_add_client_name','Scott C. Anderson MA, ATC '),(628,125,'_testimonial_0_add_client_name','field_569f3780b2f33'),(629,125,'testimonial_0_add_client_designation','Director of Athletic Training<br />\r\n											Stanford University Sports Medicine'),(630,125,'_testimonial_0_add_client_designation','field_569f379ab2f34'),(631,125,'testimonial_0_add_feedback','In my opinion, the EYE-SYNC device has significant implications for sideline evaluation, and I can see in the future every pro, college, and high  school team having one on the field.\"'),(632,125,'_testimonial_0_add_feedback','field_569f37b8b2f35'),(633,125,'testimonial_1_add_background_image','122'),(634,125,'_testimonial_1_add_background_image','field_569f36bfb2f30'),(635,125,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_title','US Army'),(636,125,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_title','field_569f36a4b2f2f'),(637,125,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_image','124'),(638,125,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_image','field_569f36d9b2f31'),(639,125,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_content',''),(640,125,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_content','field_569f36f7b2f32'),(641,125,'testimonial_1_add_client_name','Dallas C. Hack MD, MPH'),(642,125,'_testimonial_1_add_client_name','field_569f3780b2f33'),(643,125,'testimonial_1_add_client_designation','Colonel, US Army, Retired'),(644,125,'_testimonial_1_add_client_designation','field_569f379ab2f34'),(645,125,'testimonial_1_add_feedback','One of the critical gaps in assessing the sequellae of brain injury is an objective test of brain function in a form factor suitable for austere settings.  Studies on eye movement after injury indicate that eye movement is a sensitive, objective indicator of an alteration in brain function that usually returns to preinjury levels ov