 accurate.'),(2905,311,'_service_1_add_text_after_logo','field_569e0786866f1'),(2906,311,'service_1_add_content','EYE-SYNC measurement technologies have been developed over decades of research and implemented on state-of-the-art VR hardware platforms.'),(2907,311,'_service_1_add_content','field_569e07a3866f2'),(2908,311,'service_1_add_thumbnail__image','112'),(2909,311,'_service_1_add_thumbnail__image','field_569e07b9866f3'),(2910,311,'service_2_add_logo_image','94'),(2911,311,'_service_2_add_logo_image','field_569e076e866f0'),(2912,311,'service_2_add_text_after_logo','is reliable.'),(2913,311,'_service_2_add_text_after_logo','field_569e0786866f1'),(2914,311,'service_2_add_content','SyncThink has tested its metrics on over 10,000 soldiers and athletes and shown a greater than 0.8 test-retest reliability - far exceeding other cognitive tests'),(2915,311,'_service_2_add_content','field_569e07a3866f2'),(2916,311,'service_2_add_thumbnail__image','113'),(2917,311,'_service_2_add_thumbnail__image','field_569e07b9866f3'),(2918,311,'service','3'),(2919,311,'_service','field_569e075f866ef'),(2920,311,'add_test_demo_title','Test Demo '),(2921,311,'_add_test_demo_title','field_569e082f031e7'),(2922,311,'add_test_demo_content','This is a demonstration of the actual test used in the EYE-SYNC technology. Hit play to see the test in real time - dont stray far, it takes less than a minute.'),(2923,311,'_add_test_demo_content','field_569e0849031e8'),(2924,311,'add_video_source','https://vimeo.com/141831446'),(2925,311,'_add_video_source','field_569e0b0ead905'),(2926,311,'add_video_image','114'),(2927,311,'_add_video_image','field_569e0b6bad906'),(2928,311,'add_environment_title','Where and when you need it'),(2929,311,'_add_environment_title','field_569e0cf4ab817'),(2930,311,'add_environment_sub_title','In the clinic or at the point of injury'),(2931,311,'_add_environment_sub_title','field_569e0d2cab818'),(2932,311,'add_environment_content','Cognitive assessment tools are tedious, inaccurate, or immobile. EYE-SYNC delivers world-class clinical tools from the playing field to the battlefield. Follow-up with the same toolset in a clinical setting to determine return-to-activity evaluation.'),(2933,311,'_add_environment_content','field_569e0d3cab819'),(2934,311,'slider_0_add_title','Clinic'),(2935,311,'_slider_0_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(2936,311,'slider_0_add_image','115'),(2937,311,'_slider_0_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(2938,311,'slider_0_add_over_text','The EYE-SYNC <br />follows patients from the<br /> field into the clinician\'s office.<br /> Our reliability and precision<br /> allows the user to track<br /> performance back to <br />recovery.'),(2939,311,'_slider_0_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(2940,311,'slider_1_add_title','Playing Field '),(2941,311,'_slider_1_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(2942,311,'slider_1_add_image','116'),(2943,311,'_slider_1_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(2944,311,'slider_1_add_over_text','Coaches and trainers <br /> need to make fast on-field<br /> decisions that might place an <br /> athlete in harm\'s way. The EYE-SYNC<br /> is a mobile, objective assessment <br /> that provides clarity after <br /> an injury.'),(2945,311,'_slider_1_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(2946,311,'slider_2_add_title','Battlefield'),(2947,311,'_slider_2_add_title','field_569e0db4ab81c'),(2948,311,'slider_2_add_image','117'),(2949,311,'_slider_2_add_image','field_569e0d89ab81b'),(2950,311,'slider_2_add_over_text','EYE-SYNC is a<br /> functional assessment that <br /> provides real-time information to <br /> commanders on the battlefield. Spot <br /> and care for injury before it <br /> becomes a danger to the <br />mission.'),(2951,311,'_slider_2_add_over_text','field_569e0dd0ab81d'),(2952,311,'slider','3'),(2953,311,'_slider','field_569e0d69ab81a'),(2954,311,'list_0_image','118'),(2955,311,'_list_0_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(2956,311,'list_1_image','119'),(2957,311,'_list_1_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(2958,311,'list_2_image','120'),(2959,311,'_list_2_image','field_569e2e7819f97'),(2960,311,'list','3'),(2961,311,'_list','field_569e2e6719f96'),(2962,311,'testimonial_0_add_background_image','121'),(2963,311,'_testimonial_0_add_background_image','field_569f36bfb2f30'),(2964,311,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_title','Stanford University'),(2965,311,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_title','field_569f36a4b2f2f'),(2966,311,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_image','123'),(2967,311,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_image','field_569f36d9b2f31'),(2968,311,'testimonial_0_add_testimonial_content','Stanford Sports Medicine uses EYE-SYNC technology currently to screen athletes for concussion and make decisions on return to play.'),(2969,311,'_testimonial_0_add_testimonial_content','field_569f36f7b2f32'),(2970,311,'testimonial_0_add_client_name','Scott C. Anderson MA, ATC '),(2971,311,'_testimonial_0_add_client_name','field_569f3780b2f33'),(2972,311,'testimonial_0_add_client_designation','Director of Athletic Training<br />\r\n											Stanford University Sports Medicine'),(2973,311,'_testimonial_0_add_client_designation','field_569f379ab2f34'),(2974,311,'testimonial_0_add_feedback','In my opinion, the EYE-SYNC device has significant implications for sideline evaluation, and I can see in the future every pro, college, and high  school team having one on the field.\"'),(2975,311,'_testimonial_0_add_feedback','field_569f37b8b2f35'),(2976,311,'testimonial_1_add_background_image','122'),(2977,311,'_testimonial_1_add_background_image','field_569f36bfb2f30'),(2978,311,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_title','US Army'),(2979,311,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_title','field_569f36a4b2f2f'),(2980,311,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_image','124'),(2981,311,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_image','field_569f36d9b2f31'),(2982,311,'testimonial_1_add_testimonial_content',''),(2983,311,'_testimonial_1_add_testimonial_content','field_569f36f7b2f32'),(2984,311,'testimonial_1_add_client_name','Dallas C. Hack MD, MPH'),(2985,311,'_testimonial_1_add_client_name','field_569f3780b2f33'),(2986,311,'testimonial_1_add_client_designation','Colonel, US Army, Retired'),(2987,311,'_testimonial_1_add_client_designation','field_569f379ab2f34'),(2988,311,'testimonial_1_add_feedback','One of the critical gaps in assessing the sequellae of brain injury is an objective test of brain function in a form factor suitable for austere settings.  Studies on eye movement after injury indicate that eye movement is a sensitive, objective indicator of an alteration in brain function that usually returns to preinjury levels over time after an injury. Clinical trials have demonstrated high sensitivity of smooth pursuit eye movement, which is assessed by the EYE-SYNC, after an external force to the head. '),(2989,311,'_testimonial_1_add_feedback','field_569f37b8b2f35'),(2990,311,'testimonial','2'),(2991,311,'_testimonial','field_569f3690b2f2e'),(2992,312,'_wp_attached_file','2016/02/hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1.jpg'),(2993,312,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:7824;s:6:\"height\";i:4296;s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"2016/02/hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:6:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1-300x165.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:165;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1-768x422.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:422;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:37:\"hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1-1024x562.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:562;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:36:\"hack-testimonial-bg@2x-1-672x372.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:672;s:6:\"height\";i:372;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:25:\"twen