n the medical and food industries.'),(3958,409,'_team_member_detail_1_add_content','field_56a09933429f7'),(3959,409,'team_member_detail_2_add_image','176'),(3960,409,'_team_member_detail_2_add_image','field_56a098c6429f4'),(3961,409,'team_member_detail_2_add_name','Daniel Beeler'),(3962,409,'_team_member_detail_2_add_name','field_56a098f2429f5'),(3963,409,'team_member_detail_2_add_job_title','CTO'),(3964,409,'_team_member_detail_2_add_job_title','field_56a09913429f6'),(3965,409,'team_member_detail_2_add_content','Mr. Beeler joined SyncThink in 2010 and serves as CTO. Dan has been lead engineer for several companies in the Boston area and has designed technology products in large-scale data acquisition, eCommerce, and medicine. Dan holds a degree in Physics from Pomona College. He has also contributed research towards planetary science, adaptive optics, and galaxy formation at Caltech and Observatories of the Carnegie Institute of Washington. His expertise in image analysis serves as a key asset for SyncThink.'),(3966,409,'_team_member_detail_2_add_content','field_56a09933429f7'),(3967,409,'team_member_detail_3_add_image','307'),(3968,409,'_team_member_detail_3_add_image','field_56a098c6429f4'),(3969,409,'team_member_detail_3_add_name','Alan Quasha'),(3970,409,'_team_member_detail_3_add_name','field_56a098f2429f5'),(3971,409,'team_member_detail_3_add_job_title','Board Member'),(3972,409,'_team_member_detail_3_add_job_title','field_56a09913429f6'),(3973,409,'team_member_detail_3_add_content','Mr. Alan Quasha is the President of Quadrant Management, Inc., a principal investment management firm. Quadrant and its affiliates manage over $3 billion.  He is also the Co-Chairman of Carret Asset Management, LLC and Chairman of Brean Capital. Over the last 20 years, Mr. Quasha has successfully invested in over 80 companies in the United States as well as in emerging markets. Many of these investments were restructuring and turnaround situations involving significant hands-on o